  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HdtWalkGenerator
    A parser for HDT files.
    JenaOntModelMemoryWalkGenerator
    This class transforms a JenaOnt Model (or an RDF file) into the internal data structure of this framework for the walk generation process.
    MemoryWalkGenerator
    Memory based walk generator using the TripleDataSetMemory data structure.
    NtMemoryWalkGenerator
    A parser for NT files.
    NtMemoryWalkGenerator.FileReaderThread
    Thread that allows concurrent file parsing (used for data sets that consist of multiple, potentially zipped files).
    NxMemoryWalkGenerator
    Parser built with the nxparser framework.
    TdbWalkGenerator  
    TextProcessor
    Simple processor for datatpye property values.
    WalkGeneratorManager
    This class provides management (utility) functions for different walk generators, for example when it comes to deciding which walk generator to use for which file.
